      <title>朝鲜将在疫情爆发后首次开放边境旅游</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/north-korea-to-open-borders-to-tourism-in-first-since-pandemic</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜将在近五年来首次开放一般旅游，允许来自各国的外国人入境，此前该国因新冠疫情爆发而关闭了边境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/north-korea-to-open-borders-to-tourism-in-first-since-pandemic</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 13:15:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非称铁路公司业绩不佳导致失业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/transnet-south-africa-rebukes-rail-monopoly-over-performance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非政府严厉批评了经营国有货运铁路垄断企业的 Transnet SOC 有限公司的糟糕表现，称其导致这个三分之一失业的国家失去了就业机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/transnet-south-africa-rebukes-rail-monopoly-over-performance</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 12:45:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>爱沙尼亚对调查结果提出异议 中国呼吁开展“专业”调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/china-calls-for-professional-probe-as-estonia-disputes-finding</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年，爱沙尼亚一名高级官员对中国的一项调查提出质疑，并称这是一起事故。此后，中国敦促欧洲国家关注对一条重要海底管道受损事件的调查结果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/china-calls-for-professional-probe-as-estonia-disputes-finding</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 12:19:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士推动提高增值税以增加养老金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/swiss-government-pushes-for-vat-increase-to-fund-pension-boost</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士政府表示，为支持最近决定的养老金上调，政府倾向于增加国家增值税，而非提高工资缴款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/swiss-government-pushes-for-vat-increase-to-fund-pension-boost</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 12:02:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普封口费法官第三次拒绝下台请求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/trump-hush-money-judge-rejects-third-request-to-step-down</link>
      <description><![CDATA[负责监督唐纳德·特朗普封口费刑事审判的纽约法官严厉批评了最近要求他因涉嫌偏见而退出此案的努力，称其充满了“影射和错误描述”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/trump-hush-money-judge-rejects-third-request-to-step-down</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 11:57:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰陆军参谋长称对俄罗斯的进攻仍在继续</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/ukraine-s-army-chief-says-offensive-in-russia-is-continuing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰最高指挥官表示，军队正在继续在俄罗斯的进攻行动，周三在库尔斯克地区推进了 2 公里（1.2 英里）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/ukraine-s-army-chief-says-offensive-in-russia-is-continuing</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 11:25:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏丹军队缺席瑞士和谈，停火希望破灭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/sudan-army-skips-swiss-peace-talks-dashing-cease-fire-hopes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苏丹军方缺席于周三开始的由美国斡旋的谈判，这给结束这个北非国家灾难性内战的努力蒙上了一层阴影。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/sudan-army-skips-swiss-peace-talks-dashing-cease-fire-hopes</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 11:20:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国法院裁定总理在道德案件中罪名成立，将其免职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/thai-court-finds-pm-guilty-in-ethics-case-paving-way-for-ouster</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国宪法法院裁定总理斯雷塔·塔维辛违反道德规范，解除其职务，这导致这个东南亚国家陷入新一轮的政治动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/thai-court-finds-pm-guilty-in-ethics-case-paving-way-for-ouster</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 08:32:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>涉嫌参与北溪管道项目的乌克兰人逃离波兰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/germany-seeks-arrest-of-suspected-nord-stream-saboteur-sz-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰最高检察官表示，一名被德国当局怀疑参与 2022 年北溪天然气管道破坏事件的乌克兰公民在欧洲发出逮捕令后逃离波兰。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/germany-seeks-arrest-of-suspected-nord-stream-saboteur-sz-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 05:53:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球移民打击行动使留学生陷入困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/global-immigration-crackdown-ensnares-students-studying-abroad</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际学生 — — 长期以来一直是发达经济体高校的摇钱树 — — 面临着越来越不确定的未来，因为各国政府都在寻求简单的目标来控制激增的移民。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/global-immigration-crackdown-ensnares-students-studying-abroad</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
